item.description:
7 pm – Holiday Party!
8 pm – General Meeting

Come join us for a holiday party and regularly scheduled meeting. Usually we allot roughly 45 minutes for each speaker (usually 30 minutes for presentation and 15 minutes Q&A) then we begin the meeting at 8pm and discuss all the exciting happenings of the club! Come for one event, or both! However, tonight we will celebrate the holiday season. All are welcome, so please feel free to bring a friend! We will likely head out for a drink or two after the meeting, so plan to make a night of it! :D
item.how_to_find_us: Walk into 116 Beacon, down the hall & take the stairs on the left going down. Follow the signs for Boston Rotaract to the Trustee's Reading Room (TRR)!
